jected into the corona, which, in combination with the conventional\nRosner-Tucker-Vaiana scaling law, semi-analytically explains the simulation\nresults. This study refines the concepts of solar and stellar coronal heating\nand derives a theoretical relation for estimating the hidden stellar EUV\nluminosity from X-ray observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jun 2021 16:07:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 10:52:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-11"}
