y magnetohydrodynamics shock, and\ngravitational collapse of magnetized cloud core with our simulation code. The\nresults show that our numerical scheme well reproduces the dust dynamics in the\nmagnetized medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 02:41:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-18"}
