ic\nsignature. Conclusions. The neural network is a promising approach to improve\nthe interpretation of the seismic maps provided by local helioseismic\ntechniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jun 2021 10:35:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
